data.description: Welcome to your charming oasis in the heart of the Old Southside of Indianapolis! This inviting 2BR, 2BA bungalow is the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover new vinyl plank flooring that graces the living room, providing a modern touch and easy maintenance. Every room has been freshly painted, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. Beautifully updated kitchen. The upgraded bathrooms boast new tilework and sinks. Savor your morning coffee on the expansive covered porch. The fenced backyard offers a private escape with a fire pit, deck, and patio, creating the perfect setting for relaxation and entertaining. There is even room for a garden! Situated just moments away from downtown Indy, Lucas Oil Stadium, and vibrant Fountain Square.
